{
  "stem": "11133.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember having run out from the selection, and my mother returning and running up and down looking for me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, she was absolutely frantic, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can imagine, you know, what it would be like.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I'm trying to remember when he got us, finally.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Schindler actually came-- and now, see, that's another thing-- I really didn't know that, that he actually came for us, till I found out later that he-- it was only through his interference that we finally got out, you know.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because all of us-- we were lined up to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They lined us up again, and told us they were going to tattoo us-- tattoo our number on us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was even asking my mother, is it going to hurt?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Is it going to hurt?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, all of a sudden, they shoved us into the cars, and we went off without the tattoos.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We couldn't-- you know, everything was just-- everything happened, and you didn't understand why.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were there, definitely, through a lot of snow and cold.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I would have to say we were there through November and part of December.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would think so, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then it took us about three and a half days to make the trip from Auschwitz to-- my mother got very sick.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She had pneumonia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She really got very, very sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When we got to-- to Brünnlitz, you know, they came to-- Schindler came to the-- to the station to pick us up-- you know, to the railroad station-- we couldn't believe that we actually made it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we saw the men behind the wire, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we couldn't believe-- and they couldn't recognize us, because we were all shaved.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
